snippet.title: movieweb
snippet.description:
Breaking movie news since the days of dial-up. Est. 1995. MovieWeb is one of the top visited movie sites on the planet. Celebrity interviews, latest breaking movie news, rumors, and scoops. And check out our latest Top 10 lists in movies covering every nerdy aspect of Star Wars, Superhero movies, Marvel movies (MCU), DC movies (DCEU), Deadpool, Batman and so much more.

Subscribe: https://goo.gl/bpKNgt
Binge watch everything we've got.

Calling all passionate movie nerds! Want to create videos for us?
Drop us an email: support@movieweb.com

For advertising related matters, contact: ads@movieweb.com
For copyright related matters, contact: copyright@movieweb.com
